Enclosing class:
WinNT
public static class WinNT.FILE_NOTIFY_INFORMATION
extends com.sun.jna.Structure

The FILE_NOTIFY_INFORMATION structure describes the changes found by the ReadDirectoryChangesW function. This structure is non-trivial since it is a pattern stamped into a large block of result memory rather than something that stands alone or is used for input.
